{"type": "article", "id": 23621, "title": "地图也可以有情绪，这个想法来自一位纽约的设计师", "description": "汉堡店Shake Shack同样也是她的作品。", "date": "2016-03-12T08:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14, "name": "地图"}, {"id": 862, "name": "设计师"}, {"id": 24707, "name": "情绪地图"}, {"id": 10666, "name": "Pentagram"}, {"id": 24708, "name": "Paula Scher"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 190, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021611408kihT3o1K97tz4ue.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>地图设计也能玩出新花样吗？Paula Scher 是 Pentagram 的设计师之一，过去的几年里，<a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3056162/how-pentagrams-paula-scher-makes-a-map/9\">她手绘了许多地图</a>，与那些准确、实用功能强的地图不同，“我的地图不是为了表现精确，是为了表达情感”。</p>\n<p>Paula 觉得数据不仅仅是存在和不存在的问题，还是“选中”或“未被选中”的问题。她查阅了大量的数据，例如民航飞机的飞行线路，气候温度变化、 州际公路线路、城市间的驾驶时间和里程、房地产价格的中位数， ZIP 代码和区号等等，并把它们画到了地图上。每张地图都被狂热的标签和数据填满。</p>\n<p>上个月，她的这些作品在 <a href=\"http://brycewolkowitz.com/h/exhibition_images.php?e=64\">Bryce Wolfowitz Gallery</a> 画廊展出。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161127oVQlUwLbvAJRaxGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这系列作品均名为 U.S. Distances</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161128U0WuEgeVDadpSRL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">位于  Bryce Wolfowitz Gallery 的展览</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161129j5tE6BSGz4aviwq0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68493151\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">每幅地图都展示了不同的数据</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161129s8TE1RXgb6Sv2uzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70422535\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161131NPujO1HsJ8gqtr0A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67934783\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021611325ROq8AHjwJbK3fr7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67385445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>说到 Paula，她的父亲是美国地质调查局的土木工程师，受父亲影响，她自幼就对地图和数据极为痴迷。“在绘制地图的时候，我感受到了很强烈的政治因素。” 今年是选举年，从各种数据上看，她感受到了南与北、东西部之间的差异。</p>\n<p class=\"\">Paula 目前是 Pentagram 的设计师，她完成过不少的设计，例如 <a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3041777/the-untold-story-of-shake-shacks-16-billion-branding\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Shake Shack</a> 包装,\r\nthe <a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3044390/innovation-engine/pentagram-rebrands-the-new-school\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">New School</a>,\r\n <a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3032629/pentagram-rebrands-philadelphias-museum-of-art-somehow-forgets-the-rocky-stairs\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Philadelphia Museum of Art</a> 等等。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161132afZ5ptPuNSRrI243.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> Shake Shack 的新包装</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161133J0rLgeNZEMlUopFj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161134BoX9Yh8S0dLwHWDr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78864353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161134XYgBcrQdZoDfRSbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161135zxcIM75w2TauHl4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">the New School 是一所设计院校，上图中的招贴广告是 Paula 设计的</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161136rI6xF2CNgAdlXPzW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65733333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161136BRervT9Zc0if4gJd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66755674\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161137qNkO4rp8shT6tISB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161138I1JYHvLNR5GE8Zdb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64533333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Paula 的平面设计作品，Philadelphia Museum of Art </p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161139eHN3aCTI2Qd5K8lb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.484\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161139yWA0q8LVfblvSa7c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><span style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">题图来源：</span><a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3056162/how-pentagrams-paula-scher-makes-a-map/2\" style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">fastcodesign</a><br></p>\n\n"}